creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Adventskalender 2013 by Various.
Read in German by Rebecca Braunert-Plunkett; Julia Niedermaier; Elli; Claudia Salto; Karlsson; LordOider; Kara Shallenberg; Hokuspokus; Ramona Deininger-Schnabel; Herman Roskams; Kajo
Diese Sammlung ist ein Adventskalender und enthält für jeden Tag vom 1. - 24. Dezember eine Aufnahme. - Summary by Elli
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
